#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:2 beb52512c922458ca38df3378ed58f55
msgid "Wave Equation"
msgstr "波动方程"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:4 1c174782964e4aaeb36f33e876d24373
msgid ""
"A single script, ``examples/wave/wave.py``, solves the linear scalar wave "
"equation on the unit square with explicit central-difference time stepping. "
"It is the canonical hyperbolic counterpart to the heat example in "
":doc:`diffusion`."
msgstr ""
"单个脚本 ``examples/wave/wave.py`` 在单位正方形上以显式中心差分时间步进求解线性标量波动方程。它是 "
":doc:`diffusion` 中热传导示例的经典双曲型对应。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:9 21b8454a28044499b5a8aab3538dbf15
msgid "The strong form is"
msgstr "强形式为"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:11 5191e087a7774e01a82dcec33d361e6b
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"u_{tt} \\;=\\; c^2\\, \\Delta u\n"
"\\quad \\text{in } \\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad u = 0 \\text{ on } \\partial\\Omega,"
msgstr ""
"u_{tt} \\;=\\; c^2\\, \\Delta u\n"
"\\quad \\text{in } \\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad u = 0 \\text{ on } \\partial\\Omega,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:17 8147073819e148bfa86af79054fe69d5
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"with a multi-frequency Fourier-series initial condition from "
":class:`~tensormesh.dataset.WaveMultiFrequency` and zero initial velocity. "
"The script runs at :math:`c = 2.0`, :math:`\\Delta t = 10^{-3}`, for 100 "
"steps."
msgstr ""
"初始条件取自 :class:`~tensormesh.dataset.WaveMultiFrequency` 的多频傅里叶级数，初速度为零。脚本以 "
":math:`c = 2.0`\\ 、\\ :math:`\\Delta t = 10^{-3}` 运行 100 步。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:24 a94a27e732b34fa1bcbf05a91fe6b497
msgid "Central-difference time stepping"
msgstr "中心差分时间步进"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:26 f4b099f4c2834295aac5aec9a2fb2d53
msgid "The standard discretization in time is"
msgstr "标准的时间离散为"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:28 b670f4710c784af98717021ca41ed0bd
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"M\\, U^{n+1}\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"2\\, M\\, U^{n} - M\\, U^{n-1} - \\Delta t^2\\, c^2\\, A\\, U^{n},"
msgstr ""
"M\\, U^{n+1}\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"2\\, M\\, U^{n} - M\\, U^{n-1} - \\Delta t^2\\, c^2\\, A\\, U^{n},"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:34 754186cc7a704bf2aabee0cabcc231b5
msgid ""
"where :math:`M` is the mass matrix and :math:`A` is the Laplace stiffness. "
"This is **explicit** in time — at each step we solve against a fixed mass "
"matrix only, so factorize-once / back-sub-many is the right pattern."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`M` 是质量矩阵，\\ :math:`A` 是拉普拉斯刚度。这在时间上是\\ **显式**\\ "
"的——每一步只需对一个固定的质量矩阵求解，因此“分解一次 / 多次回代”才是正确的模式。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:39 2100ad2ba8a2422485aa468c666a89c3
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The first step needs special treatment because :math:`U^{-1}` is unknown; "
"using the Taylor expansion :math:`U^{-1} \\approx U^{0} - \\Delta t\\, "
"V^{0}` and the initial condition :math:`V^{0} = 0` gives"
msgstr ""
"第一步需要特殊处理，因为 :math:`U^{-1}` 未知；利用泰勒展开 :math:`U^{-1} \\approx U^{0} - \\Delta"
" t\\, V^{0}` 以及初始条件 :math:`V^{0} = 0`\\ ，得到"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:44 b2e05b9924fc45d4a7409d6e6d460eee
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"2\\, M\\, U^{1}\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"2\\, M\\, U^{0} - \\Delta t^2\\, c^2\\, A\\, U^{0}."
msgstr ""
"2\\, M\\, U^{1}\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"2\\, M\\, U^{0} - \\Delta t^2\\, c^2\\, A\\, U^{0}."

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:52 eb623d2628ae4b6ab6e0f2cc01effa9a
msgid "TensorMesh setup"
msgstr "TensorMesh 设置"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:54 18c5f874759e47bea8e33e1a3ac1df2c
msgid ""
"Two tiny assemblers (one for :math:`M`, one for :math:`A`), one "
":class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` for the homogeneous Dirichlet BC, and a "
"15-line time loop. Note the small helper that scales a "
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix` while keeping the ``SparseMatrix`` "
"type:"
msgstr ""
"两个极小的装配器（一个用于 :math:`M`\\ ，一个用于 :math:`A`\\ ）、一个用于齐次狄利克雷边界条件的 "
":class:`~tensormesh.Condenser`\\ ，以及一个 15 行的时间循环。注意那个对 "
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix` 做缩放、同时保持 ``SparseMatrix`` 类型的小辅助函数："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:60 eae1afa29f7e46c396ed8d6c5fb35ba7
msgid "examples/wave/wave.py"
msgstr "examples/wave/wave.py"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:97 6fb9a8d328474f808ae21e6afabdf33a
msgid "A few practical notes:"
msgstr "几点实用说明："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:99 484e7636a123402c9c8eec6dfeb0f5f0
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**Stability.** Central differences are conditionally stable — :math:`\\Delta"
" t \\lesssim h / c`. The script's choice (:math:`\\Delta t = 10^{-3}`, "
":math:`h = 0.01`, :math:`c = 2`) satisfies this comfortably."
msgstr ""
"**稳定性。** 中心差分是条件稳定的——:math:`\\Delta t \\lesssim h / c`\\ 。脚本所取的参数（\\ "
":math:`\\Delta t = 10^{-3}`\\ 、\\ :math:`h = 0.01`\\ 、\\ :math:`c = 2`\\ "
"）能轻松满足该条件。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:103 e35eabf81c7a49a689fdf26375a972c3
msgid ""
"**Factorize once.** ``M_`` (the condensed mass matrix) is recovered from the"
" first-step matrix and reused in every loop iteration; only the RHS changes."
msgstr "**分解一次。** ``M_``\\ （凝聚后的质量矩阵）从第一步的矩阵中恢复，并在每次循环迭代中重复使用；只有右端项发生变化。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:106 546b180c36ec40e1a458d84bda254e5e
msgid ""
"**GPU-ready.** The script picks ``cuda`` when available and "
"``mesh.to(device)`` moves the entire mesh + buffers in one call. Snapshots "
"are moved back to CPU only at the end for visualization."
msgstr ""
"**支持 GPU。** 脚本在可用时选择 ``cuda``\\ ，\\ ``mesh.to(device)`` "
"一次调用即可将整个网格及缓冲区移动过去。快照仅在最后为可视化才移回 CPU。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:111 16ac7b768c6446cb941bf816367828de
msgid ""
"For a higher-order time integrator (Newmark, Runge-Kutta) drop in "
":class:`~tensormesh.ode.ExplicitRungeKutta` from :mod:`tensormesh.ode` — see"
" :doc:`../user_guide/time_integration`."
msgstr ""
"如需使用高阶时间积分器（Newmark、龙格-库塔），可直接换用 "
":class:`~tensormesh.ode.ExplicitRungeKutta`\\ （来自 :mod:`tensormesh.ode`\\ "
"）—— 参见 :doc:`../user_guide/time_integration`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:123 d150d0a80201465f801cc818e5bd4884
msgid ""
"*Output of* ``wave.py``: *FEM prediction (left) vs analytical solution "
"(right) for a multi-frequency standing wave on the unit square. Phase and "
"amplitude track the analytical reference throughout the run; central "
"differences preserve energy as long as the CFL condition is satisfied.*"
msgstr ""
"*``wave.py`` 的输出*\\ ：\\ "
"*单位正方形上多频驻波的有限元预测（左）与解析解（右）对比。在整个运行过程中，相位和振幅都紧跟解析参考解；只要满足 CFL "
"条件，中心差分就能保持能量守恒。*"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:131 880feb6920c049948d796f666e386aaa
msgid "Energy conservation"
msgstr "能量守恒"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:133 076d9dd3df62497f8244c9f43b3ba4f0
msgid "The undamped wave equation conserves the mechanical energy"
msgstr "无阻尼波动方程守恒机械能"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:135 4da6b65aa30947f7aa2b0c40cd44c804
msgid ""
"E \\;=\\; \\underbrace{\\tfrac12\\, v^\\top M\\, v}_{\\text{kinetic}}\n"
"     \\;+\\; \\underbrace{\\tfrac12\\, u^\\top (c^2 A)\\, u}_{\\text{potential}},"
msgstr ""
"E \\;=\\; \\underbrace{\\tfrac12\\, v^\\top M\\, v}_{\\text{kinetic}}\n"
"     \\;+\\; \\underbrace{\\tfrac12\\, u^\\top (c^2 A)\\, u}_{\\text{potential}},"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:140 f06bcfbd4a6f4f4da149628fe46b372e
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"with the velocity :math:`v = u_t` taken as the centered difference of the "
"stored displacement history. ``wave.py`` evaluates this at every step and "
"writes ``wave_energy.png`` — a direct check on the time stepping, since the "
"central-difference scheme conserves a discrete energy up to "
":math:`\\mathcal{O}(\\Delta t^2)` whenever the CFL condition holds."
msgstr ""
"其中速度 :math:`v = u_t` 取为所存储位移历史的中心差分。\\ ``wave.py`` 在每一步都计算它并写出 "
"``wave_energy.png``——这是对时间步进的直接检验，因为只要 CFL 条件成立，中心差分格式就能在 "
":math:`\\mathcal{O}(\\Delta t^2)` 精度内守恒一个离散能量。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/wave.rst:151 f75a14bab3e74650a74f1d417acb1c58
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Kinetic and potential energy exchange out of phase while the total (red) "
"stays flat: the relative drift over the 100-step run is about "
":math:`1.5\\times10^{-3}`. The motion starts as pure potential energy (zero "
"initial velocity) and equipartitions as the standing wave develops."
msgstr ""
"动能与势能反相交换，而总能量（红色）保持平直：100 步运行中的相对漂移约为 :math:`1.5\\times10^{-3}`\\ "
"。运动起始时为纯势能（初速度为零），随着驻波形成而趋于能量均分。"

